solution_code: public class Solution {--newline--    public int rangeBitwiseAnd(int m, int n) {--newline--        if(m == 0){--newline--            return 0;--newline--        }--newline--        int moveFactor = 1;--newline--        while(m != n){--newline--            m >>= 1;--newline--            n >>= 1;--newline--            moveFactor <<= 1;--newline--        }--newline--        return m * moveFactor;--newline--    }--newline--}
